== 聯絡方式 Contact Us ==

   如果您有任何建議或是任何 bug 想要回報，請使用 github 的 Issues 功能。您也可以透過 email 寄信到 info@hypo.cc，我們超喜歡你們的回響的！
   
   If you have any suggestion or bugs to report, please use the Issues Tab in the github. You can also contact us via email, just send your opinion to info@hypo.cc We're a big fans of users feedbacks!

